{"tid":2075911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被指和你shop搶犯 20歲男生襲警罪不成立","createTime":"2020-06-23T06:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T14:02:39.000Z","uid":272922,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cf7f4601fd8796a16fcf6e720280f2b8f816d37a","tid":2075911,"uid":272922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:52:19.000Z","msg":"【被指「和你Shop」搶犯　20歲男生襲警罪名不成立】<br />\n<br />\n去年12月有網民號召在沙田新城市廣場發起「和你Shop」，警方試圖制伏疑犯時，一名男生被指為了「搶犯」襲擊警員，該男生否認一項襲警罪，他今日（6月23日）在沙田裁判法院獲判罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官李志豪裁決時指，呈堂片段能證明警長陳勁濤受襲，但未能看到是誰施襲擊。警長指被告當時髮色突出，但片中無與被告形象相若的人。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-23-2020/63831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F06-23-2020%2F63831&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7o5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=a4f0d79b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-23-2020/63831</a>"},{"pid":"dc1aeaacd110b08dfeefe849f2aee1d00dac6ba7","tid":2075911,"uid":272922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:52:51.000Z","msg":"染髮 剪髮好重要 唔準偷懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7639633af23f356deb48e0eb770cb43b4591e9ec","tid":2075911,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}